# Layout wrapper (PageShell) rules

## Must
- All pages must render their content inside `src/components/PageShell/PageShell.jsx`.
- Page wrapper must follow this structure:
  - Outer `Box`: `backgroundColor: 'background.default'`, `minHeight: '100vh'`, `py: 4`
  - Inner `Container maxWidth="lg"`
  - Content `Paper`/surface: `bgcolor: 'background.paper'`, `borderRadius: '24px'`, `px: 4`, `py: 3`
- In dark mode, the wrapper and inner surface must keep subtle layered contrast (brown-based), not a flat single tone.
- Borders/dividers should come from theme tokens (`divider`) to preserve soft depth.

## Never
- Do not copy/paste wrapper code into each page.
- Do not set page backgrounds via CSS; use theme tokens only.

